.TP 1.9i
.B SENOMAPFND
Can't open mapping database (Windows only)
.TP
.B EFAULT
Bad address
.TP
.B EINVAL
Invalid argument
.TP
.B ESTGROUP
Invalid group
.TP
.B SECONNDROP
Connection closed by remote end
.TP
.B SECOMERR
Communication error
.TP
.B SEINTERNAL
Internal error
.TP
.B SEUSERUNKN
User unknown
.TP
.B ESTLINKNAME
User link name processing error
.TP
.B SEOPNOTSUP
Operation not supported (should not happen)
.TP
.B ESTMEM
Request too big
.TP
.B ENOENT
No such file or directory
.TP
.B SESYSERR
System error
.TP
.B ESTCLEARED
Request cleared
.TP
.B ESTKILLED
Request killed
.TP
.B ENOSPC
No space left on device
.TP
.B ESTLNKNSUP
Symbolic link not supported
.TP
.B ESTNACT
Stager not active (if you specify the STAGE_NORETRY flag - default is to retry forever)
.TP
.B SENOSHOST
Host not known
.TP
.B SETIMEDOUT
